Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吧 好好展現一下北宇治的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}表演得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是哪所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會吧 北宇治？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們有這麼優秀嗎
